<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038494" n="1"/>
<lb/><opener>Viro Illustrissimo et Doctissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person"><subst><del>A</del><add>P</add></subst>etro Antonio
                              <lb/>Michelotti</rs>. <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>Nic.</abbr> <abbr>B.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Rogo ut me excusatum habeas, Vir Amicissime, quod tam
      <lb/>tarde respondeam ad <rs key="B_1718-11-03_991170517052005501" type="letter">ultimas</rs> Tuas <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1718-11-03">3. hujus mensis</date> ad me
                              <lb/>datas. Adscribas hanc moram tum negotiis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sub initium
                              <lb/>hujus novi studii partim meis Lectionibus, partim auscultatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ni Lectionum aliorum Professorum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me impendenda sunt;
                              <lb/>tum advers<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudini in quam recidi et qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> me <date when="1718-11-07">nudius ter<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tius</date> per totum diem lecto affixum tenuit. Laboro adhuc dum
                              <lb/>capite et stomacho, et nisi hic rite suo officio in posterum fun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gi velit, cogar invitus remedia purgantia adhibere.</p>
<p><lb/>Sed ecce brevem responsionem ad dubia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi proposuisti
      <lb/>circa nugas <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keillanas</rs>. Primo scias oportet in his numeris 1,659; 
                              <lb/>132, 72; 0,73; 0,4187;<del> fig</del> notas qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> script<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt post co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a
                              <lb/>denotare fractiones decimales, et unius cujusque figur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad si<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nistram posite valorem <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quoad unitates suas<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> semper esse
                              <lb/>decuplo majorem, quam valor<del>em</del> ejus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est ad dextram,
                              <lb/>quemadmodum etiam res se habet in notis ante co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a positis;
                              <lb/>Ita 1,659 nihil aliud est quam <formula>1\frac{659}{1000}</formula>; 132,72 nihil aliud
                              <lb/>quam <formula>132\frac{72}{100}</formula>; 0,73 nihil aliud quam <formula>\frac{73}{100}</formula>; 0,4187 nihil
                              <lb/>aliud quam <formula>\frac{4187}{10000}</formula>. Harum fractionum decimalium expli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cationem et algorithmum invenies in <rs key="biblio_BTGHJ64J" type="biblio">Arithmetica</rs> universali
      <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoni</rs>, ab initio; Deinde quando dicit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keil</rs> unciam unam
                                    <lb/>sanguinis esse <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem <cit><quote><foreign xml:lang="eng"><hi rend="u">in bulk to 1,659 inches</hi></foreign></quote></cit>, vult dicere
                              <lb/>soliditatem vel volumen unci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quari uni digito<del> <gap/></del> cubico,
                              <pb facs="1038495" n="2"/>
<lb/>et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea <formula>\frac{659}{1000}</formula> unius digiti cubici, nam terminus iste An<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>glicus <foreign xml:lang="eng"><hi rend="u">bulk</hi></foreign> refertur ad soliditatem; unde octoginta unci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalent 132,72, sive 132 digitis cubicis et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea <formula>\frac{72}{100}</formula> uni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>us digiti cubici. Tertio erras in eo quod putes, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keillium</rs> dixisse
                              <lb/>numerum hunc 0,4187 esse quadratum hujus 0,73; nam
                              <lb/>ad habendam aream orificii circularis aort<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex data dia<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>metro 0,73, non sumendum est quadratum diametri, sed 
                              <lb/>debet dimidia diam<subst><del>t</del><add>et</add></subst>er duci in di<subst><del>a</del><add>m</add></subst>idiam peripheriam; quare
      <lb/>secundum rationem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118503863">Archimedeam</rs> diametri ad periphepheriam
                                    <lb/>7 ad 22, quam rationem <rs type="person">Keilium</rs> adhibuisse video, inve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nietur quantitas orificii aort<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 0,4187 (neglecto residuo)
                              <lb/>sive <formula>\frac{4187}{10000}</formula> partes unius digiti quadrati; quapropter si divi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>das totum cylindrum sanguinis, id est, 132,72, per<del> 0,4187;</del>
<lb/><del>sive </del>basin suam id est per 0,4187; sive <formula>132\frac{72}{100}</formula> per
                              <lb/><formula>\frac{4187}{10000}</formula>; invenies <add>pro</add> longitudine hujus cylindri 316 digitos
      <lb/>(neglecto iterum residuo) aut 26 pedes, uti asseruit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keillius</rs>.
      <lb/>Sed miror Te dicere, quod non intelligas illa<del> q</del> verba <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keillii</rs>,
                              <lb/>quibus asserit velocitatem sanguinis propter Diastolem
                              <lb/>duplo majoris <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimari debere. Nam quia tempore unius
                              <lb/>minuti ponit fieri 80 contractiones cordis, fient etiam eodem
                              <lb/>tempore 80 dilatationes, quare si tempus contractionis tan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum durare ponatur quantum tempus dilat<subst><del>i</del><add>a</add></subst>tionis, mani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>festum est, illas octoginta uncias in aortam influentes
                              <lb/>pro transitu suo in aortam requirere tantum tempus dimidii
                              <lb/>minuti, quia alterum dimidium impenditur dilat<subst><del>i</del><add>a</add></subst>tioni
                              <pb facs="1038497" n="3"/>
<lb/>cordis, quo t<subst><del>a</del><add>e</add></subst>mpore nullus fit influxus sanguinis. Ideo veloci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tas sanguinis (per supposita <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Keillii</rs>) <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimanda est, ac si
                              <lb/>describeret uno dimidio minuti 26 pedes, sive uno minuto 52
      <lb/>pedes. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c ad interrogata Tua. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzerus</rs> noster mihi
                              <lb/>scripsit, sibi nuntiatum esse, <abbr>Ill.mum</abbr> et <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">mum</hi></abbr> Equi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089586140">Maurocenum</rs><del> sibique</del> exorari se passum fuisse, ne
                              <lb/>se futur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <subst><del>E</del><add>e</add></subst>lectioni opponeret; aveo scire, num huic
                              <lb/>nuntio fidendum sit. Alius porro mihi advenit l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus
                                          <lb/>nuntius, qui et Tibi gratissimus erit; nempe Patruelem
      <lb/>meum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Nicolaum</rs> electum esse Professorem Matheseos
                                    <lb/>in Universitate qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est <rs key="place_GEO-2934691" type="place">Duisburgi ad Rhenum</rs>, et 
      <lb/>nihil aliud expectari nisi confirmationem <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118535978">Regis Prus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>si<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, cui subdita est illa Civitas. Sed rogo ut dissimules
      <lb/>Te ista scire, donec ipse <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelis</rs> meus a<subst><del>d</del><add>ut</add></subst> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs>
<lb/>idem Tibi significent.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale et fave.</salute> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place"><abbr>Patav.</abbr></rs> <date when="1718-11-09">9. <abbr>9bris</abbr> 1718</date>.</closer>
</div>
